rows.label: tlk70000046_01_msg0001
rows.name: Dammit. I'm out of items for my pouch.

rows.label: tlk70000046_01_msg0002
rows.name:
It's not like it's the end of the world
or anything, but they do make life on
the road a little easier.

rows.label: tlk70000046_01_msg0003
rows.name:
If you leverage the effects of the right
items, you can really amp up your
usefulness. For a bit, anyway.

rows.label: tlk70000046_01_msg0004
rows.name:
At least it looks like I'm going to be
able to finish up here without too
much trouble.

rows.label: tlk70000046_01_msg0005
rows.name:
You should be loading up your pouches
with stuff as well. Just keep an eye on
how much you have left.
